00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:13.500
So this is interesting.

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:16.520
This is kind of assuming that
the only way to get stronger

00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:17.530
is by eating spinach.

00:01:17.530 --> 00:01:19.590
But that's not what that
first statement says.

00:01:19.590 --> 00:01:21.350
That first statement
