00:01:33.370 --> 00:01:34.660
Maybe you eat eggs.

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:38.900
Who knows?

00:01:38.900 --> 00:01:43.585
There's a million, you know--
maybe you have a-- drink milk.

00:01:43.585 --> 00:01:44.210
Who knows what?

00:01:44.210 --> 00:01:49.270
There are a lot of options
that will get you stronger.

00:01:49.270 --> 00:01:50.690
Drink milk.

00:01:50.690 --> 00:01:53.320
So eating spinach
