00:02:38.170 --> 00:02:39.610
"You are not stronger.

00:02:39.610 --> 00:02:41.520
Therefore, you must not
have eaten spinach."

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:44.020
And we have to be very
careful to separate

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:45.970
our everyday
experience versus what

00:02:45.970 --> 00:02:47.970
