et cetera, et cetera.

00:02:59.230 --> 00:03:01.970
But we have to remember, we're
assuming this first statement

00:03:01.970 --> 00:03:02.740
is true.

00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:05.350
We're assuming this first
statement is absolutely true.

00:03:05.350 --> 00:03:08.260
Eating spinach
makes you stronger.

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:10.900
